{"lastModified":1774446788973,"uri":"c::7819298091::vessel::d5cabfd0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey, Aegean Sea\n\nThe S Dogu is a 32-meter deluxe gulet that was built in 2006 and underwent a major renovation in 2014. It is a custom-made sailing yacht/motor-sailer or \"gulet\" that combines traditional Turkish craftsmanship with modern luxury. Based in Marmaris, Turkey, it is available for charter in the beautiful and historic Aegean Sea.\n\nThe S Dogu features six well-appointed cabins that can comfortably accommodate up to 12 guests. The cabins include two master suites and four double cabins, each with its own en-suite bathroom. The yacht's interior is beautifully finished with warm wood paneling and elegant furnishings, creating a welcoming and sophisticated atmosphere for guests.\n\nOn the deck, the S Dogu offers a variety of spaces for relaxation and entertainment. The spacious flybridge is equipped with a Jacuzzi where guests can soak in the warm waters and enjoy the stunning views of the Turkish coastline. The yacht's interior features a fully equipped entertainment system, including a DVD/CD player, an iPod docking station, LCD TVs, and a satellite TV system. There is also Wi-Fi access throughout the yacht.\n\nFor those looking for water-based activities, the S Dogu has a range of water toys, including a donut, sea kayak, snorkeling gear, wakeboard, water skis, and a tube. There is also fishing gear available for those who wish to catch some local fish.\n\nThe S Dogu is crewed by a friendly and professional team of five, who are dedicated to ensuring that guests have a memorable and enjoyable experience on board. With its elegant design, luxurious amenities, and prime location, the S Dogu is an ideal choice for those seeking a first-class yacht charter in the stunning waters of the Aegean Sea.","blueprint":{"name":"S DOGU","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819298091::vessel::d5cabfd0-fe8c